HEADWORD: Tintinnabulary
<hw>Tin`tin*nab"u*la*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>tintinnabulum</ets> a little bell, fr.
<ets>tintinnare</ets> to ring, to jingle, <ets>tinnire</ets> to
jingle.]</ety> <def>Having or making the sound of a bell;
tinkling.</def>⟦br⟧
